Thinking back on one of the most surreal experiences I’ve ever had that I am so grateful for. It truly feels like a wild dream that I was blessed enough to be asked to sing background vocals for one of the most legendary artists of all time miss @ladygaga not to mention the incredible band that included icons @nilerodgers and @raphael_saadiq . It was an honor to be a part of the tribute to David Bowie’s life at the 58th Grammy Awards♥️ I’ll never forget this medley. It’s burned into my brain forever and I’m so happy about it ✨ #ladygaga #grammys #backgroundsinger #singing #davidbowie
